      "comment": "ARCHIE MCIVOR (5) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by 1.5 lengths at this track in a handy 19.64 beating Black Tycoon. Awkwardly drawn but has the ability and in winning form. Comes through a solid form race last start. Can measure up again. WALTER WALRUS (7) placed three back at this track then out of the placings last couple but moves to box 7 this time where he has performed well. Can improve sharply here. DIM SIM NODDY (1) has been without a win for a while, the latest jumping from an outside draw when fifth (17.15) at this track in a Grade 5. Can do much better this time. WILD SAL (2) will need to run right up to last start to feature again.",
